<cb:div type="cbeta-notes">
<head>CBETA 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0276001A" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0276001A">別古本無舉字下同</note>
<note n="0276001B" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0276001B">別古本無拈云二字下同</note>
<note n="0278001" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0278001">魯等六字別古本作空劫<choice cb:resp="#resp1"><corr>已</corr><sic>巳</sic></choice>前承當頭頂天佛未出世時會取脚踏地王老師</note>
<note n="0279006A" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0279006A">洛等八字別古本在於魚字下</note>
<note n="0279006B" resp="#resp3" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0279006B">別古本未下更有可惜許臨濟兒孫七<choice cb:resp="#resp1"><corr>字</corr><sic>宇</sic></choice></note>
</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0276001A" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0276001A">別古本無舉及拈云三字下同</note>
<note n="0276001B" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0276001B">別古本無舉及拈云三字下同</note>
<note n="0276002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0276002">處下別古本有這裡看不透且請歸堂喫茶去十二字</note>
<note n="0276003" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0276003">識下別古本有帝不契渡江至魏七字</note>
<note n="0276004" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0276004">字下別古本有如鐵掃<g ref="#CB00416">󰆠</g>相似復云八字</note>
<note n="0276005" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0276005">云下別古本有拈花傅妙旨老頭陀徹底承當十二字</note>
<note n="0276006" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0276006">碎下別古本有大似晴空激電白日見星十字</note>
<note n="0276007" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0276007">試等十一字別古本作不是百丈利齒獰牙多為野狐善果遂也</note>
<note n="0276008" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0276008">生擒活捉四字別古本作放開捏聚</note>
<note n="0276009" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0276009">且等八字別古本作有人識得南泉便入慈心三昧十一字</note>
<note n="0277001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0277001">云下別古本有逸志田畦放情草澤天童所謂鼻孔纍垂信飽餐者也修山主二十四字</note>
<note n="0277002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0277002">者僧二字無</note>
<note n="0277003" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0277003">如等十一字作只饒口譚玄以稼穡作佛事要與地藏比肩</note>
<note n="0277004" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0277004">滹沱二字別古本作玄師</note>
<note n="0277005" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0277005">然等十一字作正法眼向瞎驢邊滅却分明露出半班要得完全待臨濟眼光落地</note>
<note n="0277006" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0277006">云下別古本有眼如瞎耳如聾諸聖去處點不成畫不就二老行藏還知彼落處麼正是憐兒不覺醜</note>
<note n="0277007" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0277007">子下別古本有善丹青者將此四老製作一圖畫是非窠臼自然瓦解氷消二十三字</note>
<note n="0277008" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0277008">云下別古本有問如石火答似電光然遲遲速似同精光間有彷彿非山主久參耆德不能辨也三十字</note>
<note n="0277009" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0277009">道等八字別古本作無字是趙州關有字是趙州劍</note>
<note n="0277010" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0277010">公下別古本有遊盡幾多山水心思疲極十字</note>
<note n="0277011" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0277011">知下有地藏不費些兒鹽醋八字</note>
<note n="0277012" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0277012">後等六字作正如畵龍點睛則破壁飛去法眼便拜</note>
<note n="0278001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278001">魯等六字別古本作空劫巳前承當頭頂天佛未出世時會取脚踏地王老師</note>
<note n="0278002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278002">王老師三字作魯祖</note>
<note n="0278003" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278003">要下有不待啟齒膾炙哉膾炙哉十字</note>
<note n="0278004" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278004">云下別古本有驚人之句破格之機雪峰父子多磊落也十六字</note>
<note n="0278005" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278005">鼻下有動着則三字</note>
<note n="0278006" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278006">宗下有則芟為兩段五字</note>
<note n="0278007" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278007">一條二字別古本無</note>
<note n="0278008" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278008">牛下有穿過二字</note>
<note n="0278009" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278009">＊攔等六字作鼻孔待者犀牛穿過諸人鼻孔（＊印ノ字ハ本文ト異ナル。<g ref="#CB18834">󴦒</g>）</note>
<note n="0278010" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278010">福下有的的二字</note>
<note n="0278011" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278011">繩等八字作條犀牛來不知彼是何拴索</note>
<note n="0278012" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278012">且等二十字別古本無</note>
<note n="0278013" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278013">去下別古本有看他印箇甚麼六字</note>
<note n="0278014" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0278014">壞下別古本有皮穿觔骨露分明向你道十字</note>
<note n="0279001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279001">鎻下別古本有渾無彼此而善解環心自然十一字</note>
<note n="0279002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279002">向等十六字作信位人悉寐語也</note>
<note n="0279003" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279003">雪竇拈三字別古本無</note>
<note n="0279004" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279004">穴下有垂字</note>
<note n="0279005" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279005">更等十二字別古本作拄杖子隨宜得用用得看一馬生三寅</note>
<note n="0279006A" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279006A">洛等八字別古本在於魚字下而未下更有可惜許臨濟兒孫七宇</note>
<note n="0279006B" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279006B">洛等八字別古本在於魚字下而未下更有可惜許臨濟兒孫七宇</note>
<note n="0279007" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279007">云下別古本有吞不下吐不出六字</note>
<note n="0279008" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279008">院等四字在於毛字下</note>
<note n="0279009" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279009">勤下有不着便三字</note>
<note n="0279010" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279010">致問二字無</note>
<note n="0279011" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279011">慈作恩</note>
<note n="0279012" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279012">云下別古本有觀溈仰三字</note>
<note n="0279013" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279013">勘人二字在於溈字上</note>
<note n="0279014" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279014">醒下有耳為僧者寧無愧乎余甞評云十二字</note>
<note n="0279015" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279015">何下有譬夫貧者握金成土而富者握土成金其變動一也溈山讚善正如父子上陳又安知陳敗不禁苕掃<g ref="#CB00416">󰆠</g>耶四十一字</note>
<note n="0279016" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279016">面前二字別古本作赤肉團上</note>
<note n="0279017" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279017">云下別古本有赤身露體紙裏麻纏要是其人方分皂白十六字</note>
<note n="0279018" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279018">說作粘着</note>
<note n="0279019" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279019">日疑有</note>
<note n="0279020" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279020">券字別古本無</note>
<note n="0279021" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0279021">鹽官二字別古本作忠</note>
<note n="0280001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280001">云下別古本有打草蛇驚放鷹兔走這僧如圓珠在盤碌碌轉也若會得可謂採汲不虛施其奈皮下無血辜負三十七字</note>
<note n="0280002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280002">片作一</note>
<note n="0280003" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280003">血作好</note>
<note n="0280004" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280004">良等九字無</note>
<note n="0280005" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280005">拈云下別古本作念頭不切類羅山天下人跳出這窠臼不得這一咄字殺人不見血羅山連問頭亦瓦解氷消且道起滅者誰</note>
<note n="0280006" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280006">明等五字別古本作答處雖不近人情大有回互</note>
<note n="0280007" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280007">僧下有強出頭來殊不知七字</note>
<note n="0280008" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280008">眾等二十二字作也公案如麻繩着水一步緊一步放得下是好手</note>
<note n="0280009" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280009">萬松二字別古本作若是衲僧</note>
<note n="0280010" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0280010">從等五字作註解一遍</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
